{"tid":439991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教大幼兒系助理教授疑因選民資格被取消　恐嚇將選舉主任「碎屍萬段」","createTime":"2017-10-18T10:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T11:30:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62fedfa24bbf95414c6539d230cd285db8affd8d","tid":439991,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171018/s00001/d376087bbe460f2173bff9a7896db361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171018%2Fs00001%2Fd376087bbe460f2173bff9a7896db361.jpg&h=6e5db079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育大學幼兒教育學系一名助理教授疑因不滿選民資格被取消，兩度致電選舉事務處，留言恐嚇要將副總選舉事務主任「碎屍萬段」。助理教授被控兩項刑事恐嚇罪，案件今於東區裁判法院提堂。據悉他疑因未有更新選民資料而被取消選民資格。<br />\n<br />\n被告霍鴻桀（34歲）報稱為助理教授，暫毋須答辯。他被控於今年6月23及27日，在灣仔選舉事務處威脅沈南龍會使其人身遭受損害，意圖使他受驚。翻查資料，沈為副總選舉事務主任。<br />\n<br />\n辯方呈上被告醫療報告，並表示將去信律政司申請以其他方式處理本案。案件押至下月1日再訊，其間被告獲准以1,000元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被告疑致電到選舉事務處熱線投訴，並在留言信箱中表示要將沈「碎屍萬段」，又稱「信唔信我斬你」，職員其後報警求助。"},{"pid":"c8ab6470a0e7a5068c6553345fdc617dc756150d","tid":439991,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">站務台投訴三色貓</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"fce8f9ad2e7257596b85b63eba5b5b44b0a520aa","tid":439991,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:41:33.000Z","msg":"講女姦男殺、殺無赦嗰啲呢？"},{"pid":"e3a8bfc3a42c02a8cf92fbbd0fe5a8af5b42a798","tid":439991,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講女姦男殺、殺無赦嗰啲呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒有行動"},{"pid":"6532d85d8a2213e78a7da035954faa4881d30e10","tid":439991,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講女姦男殺、殺無赦嗰啲呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒有行動</blockquote><br />\n咁碎屍萬段有無行動？<br />\n唔係好抵死咩？"},{"pid":"139f454e4416dc3874126719cd60c0cc1db8b082","tid":439991,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"選舉主任中文差，理解能力低<br />\n碎屍萬段只係廣東話入面啜核嘅用詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12724ddcb7c4b040a37a0918629b83188ac8b4e","tid":439991,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"碎左個C字咋<br />\n識唔識中文架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962ba64db51f3463b9c7803ee20a70c6a3f097d0","tid":439991,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"只係表達出厭惡的程度，不涉及任何暴力行為。"},{"pid":"bd5aa65b7ef227ae693eff6b98337ecde020ee14","tid":439991,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"姓何個個呢？"},{"pid":"dcb8374279fa1b112c181165921ddaa337ddaff9","tid":439991,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"人地話碎條屍咋嘛，你生勾勾就唔係屍啦"}]}